data.description: Welcome to 240! This home is truly a must see if you are in the market for a 3/2 home in East Tennessee. Beautifully updated 2014 double wide with fresh paint and flooring. The home sits on a 1/2 acre with an additional 1/2 acre beside it. There is a back deck, and more space for a gazebo, fire pit, or swing set. Its time to call East Tennessee home! Call or text today.
